{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d11c139251","title":"毛泽东会见扎伊尔共和国总统蒙博托谈话记录节选","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a8f246c93a","index":0,"year":1973,"month":1,"day":13,"articleId":"d11c139251"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6da6fe2e15","type":"title","text":"毛泽东会见扎伊尔共和国总统蒙博托谈话记录节选","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"29a7882cc3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：怎么样，跑到北京住得惯吗？","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"0e3461fd74","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：很好。在这里对我们的欢迎是非常友好、热烈的。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"8281ff7025","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：卢蒙巴，他没有来过。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"006f48c69e","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：对。他没有来得及来。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"8d52b26962","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：我们是支持他的。我们还支持几个，有基赞加、谬勒尔，就是不支持你！（笑）","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"69db4fc032","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：我知道。还有一些和他们在一起的。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"b6abbbdf35","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：还有一些打游击的，给他们钱和武器。就是他们不会打，打你不赢啊，那我有啥办法啊!","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"3c2c80c69c","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：因为面对他们的是蒙博托这样有魄力的人。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"38e87b0d80","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：因为你这个帽子（指蒙戴的豹皮帽）把他们吓住了（众笑）。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"891e3a02c2","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：不是，是我的权威。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"5c14397c6c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：他们那些人我看不怎么样。不少人都在外国，不到国内去，不了解情况。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"546601f23c","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：是这样的。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"cad805e4eb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：不是我们不革命，是他们自己不争气，打你不赢有啥办法啊。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"3d7fdf31f6","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：而且他们不仅自己不争气，还用全部时间来欺骗把他们看作朋友的人。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"2458eb9d46","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：现在都完了吧。被你打得呜乎哀哉了吧。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"617c7fc390","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：现在扎伊尔是非洲中心的一个大国，享有和平，是一个巩固的国家。扎伊尔的儿女们联合起来了，拥护一个领袖，一个政党。刚才说的事情已经过去了。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"49f1d91e96","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：过去了吗？","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"48f914d93f","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：是的，这些都已经过去了，所以我们才能坐在一起共同庆祝中扎友谊。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"2d3a40189c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：怎么叫扎伊尔？","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"b1a76a9c15","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：这是我们国家原来的名字，叫扎伊尔，后来比利时殖民主义的国王利奥波德二世把它改为刚果。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"d17c576737","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：相反，我不怕，而且主张和平共处。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"9edf8f217c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：我不主张和平共处，主张革命！","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"45768890f2","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：我也在革命，用我的方式来革命。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"1fb791bd2b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：讲是那样讲，什么和平共处，五项原则，酝酿的一条就是世界要革命！","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"def10374a2","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：我们也搞革命，但按照我们的方式。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"915a12ff17","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：各有各的方式。你们搞你们的方式，我们搞我们的方式。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"081da75bc0","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：对。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"1a43d99fd6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：不隐瞒自己的观点，不讲假话。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"eafc1e151a","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：我来这里后，注意到这一点了。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"09a2f7fc81","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：比如我们跟尼克松达成的公报嘛，……","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"8af8d3896b","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：对，我读了好几遍。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"2d2198ab12","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：就是各讲各的。有几处共同的，可以合作的。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"ede9e7baa7","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙：我也注意到这一点了。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"08196ea06e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：美国人是看我们不起的。非洲人、亚洲人，他们都看不起。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"3a767fa6f6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：我们支持反对你的人。你也不隐晦，照样讲。我们也不隐晦，照样讲。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"},{"id":"8a4269be5e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：现在呢，两国就要合作了。你讲和平共处，我也没法子反对了。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251"}],"page":{"id":"e58f72756d","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d11c139251","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}